---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="Locations | Morning Tide Consulting and Collective"
	description="MCC provides remote services across 43+ PSYPACT states with efficient scheduling and premium care delivery."
>
	<main class="px-6 py-16 lg:px-10 lg:py-20">
		<section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl space-y-8">
			<p class="eyebrow">Locations</p>
			<h1 class="max-w-4xl text-5xl leading-none text-(--color-ink) sm:text-6xl">Remote services across 43+ states through PSYPACT.</h1>
			<p class="max-w-3xl text-lg leading-8 text-(--color-muted)">
				MCC provides remote evaluations with consistent standards of communication and delivery. This model supports broad geographic reach while keeping scheduling and turnaround efficient.
			</p>
		</section>

		<section class="mx-auto mt-12 grid max-w-6xl gap-6 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_1fr]">
			<div class="section-shell rounded-4xl p-8">
				<p class="eyebrow">Service Footprint</p>
				<p class="mt-4 text-base leading-8 text-(--color-muted)">
					Remote evaluations are available in 43+ PSYPACT states. Update this page with your current list of eligible states or a dynamic map once your final service map is confirmed.
				</p>
			</div>
			<div class="rounded-4xl border border-(--color-line-soft) bg-(--color-surface) p-8 shadow-(--shadow-soft)">
				<p class="eyebrow">Scheduling and Access</p>
				<ul class="mt-4 space-y-3 text-sm leading-7 text-(--color-muted)">
					<li>Remote-first service model</li>
					<li>Streamlined intake and scheduling</li>
					<li>One-week evaluation and report timeline</li>
					<li>Premium communication from intake to feedback</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>
